<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>마이페이지 | Seoyeon Tour</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * { box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; background: #f8f7f4; }

        .nav-link { color: #555 !important; font-size: 0.9rem; }
        .nav-link:hover { color: #000 !important; }

        .mypage-header {
            position: relative;
            height: 320px;
            background-image: url('/images/mypagewall.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            margin-top: 56px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: flex-start;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .mypage-header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(
                to bottom right,
                rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 0%,
                rgba(0,0,0,0.15) 100%
            );
        }
        .mypage-header-text {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 48px 56px;
        }
        .mypage-header-text .label {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .mypage-header-text h2 {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 2.0rem;
            font-weight: 350;
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .info-card {
            border: none;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
            border-radius: 16px;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .section-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #aaa;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR',sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1a1a2e;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }
        .info-table td {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        .info-table td:first-child {
            color: #888;
            width: 90px;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
        }
        .info-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }

        .payment-table th {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #aaa;
            font-weight: 400;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
        }
        .payment-table td {
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            color: #444;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
        }
        .btn-logout {
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            color: #888;
            background: transparent;
            font-size: 0.82rem;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-logout:hover { border-color: #c0392b; color: #c0392b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-white shadow-sm fixed-top px-4">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="/">SEOYEON TOUR</a>
        <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navMenu">
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navMenu">
            <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto gap-2">
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/introduce">소개</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/event">이벤트</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-europe">허니문-유럽</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/honeymoon-resort">허니문-휴양지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/group">단체여행</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/package">패키지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/reviews">후기</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="/contact">온라인문의</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item">
                    <a class="nav-link fw-bold text-dark" href="/mypage"><%= user.name %>님</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link active" href="/mypage">마이페이지</a></li>
                <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="mypage-header">
        <div class="mypage-header-text">
            <p class="label">My Page</p>
            <h2><%= user.name %>님,<br>안녕하세요</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="py-5">
        <div class="container py-3">
            <div class="row g-4">

                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="info-card p-4">
                        <p class="section-label">My Info</p>
                        <h5 class="section-title">내 정보</h5>
                        <table class="table table-borderless info-table">
                            <tr><td>이름</td><td><%= user.name %></td></tr>
                            <tr><td>아이디</td><td><%= user.user_id %></td></tr>
                            <tr><td>이메일</td><td><%= user.email || '-' %></td></tr>
                            <tr><td>전화번호</td><td><%= user.phonenum || '-' %></td></tr>
                            <tr><td>주소</td><td><%= user.address || '-' %></td></tr>
                        </table>
                        <a href="/auth/logout" class="btn btn-logout mt-3 w-100">로그아웃</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <div class="info-card p-4">
                        <p class="section-label">My Payments</p>
                        <h5 class="section-title">결제 내역</h5>
                        <% if (payments.length > 0) { %>
                            <table class="table payment-table">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>결제일</th>
                                        <th>결제 수단</th>
                                        <th>상태</th>
                                        <th>수량</th>
                                        <th>총 금액</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                    <% payments.forEach(payment => { %>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td><%= new Date(payment.paid_at).toLocaleDateString('ko-KR') %></td>
                                        <td><%= payment.pay_method || '-' %></td>
                                        <td><%= payment.payment_status || '-' %></td>
                                        <td><%= payment.quantity || '-' %></td>
                                        <td><%= payment.total_price ? Number(payment.total_price).toLocaleString() : '-' %>원</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <% }) %>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <p class="text-muted text-center py-5" style="font-size:0.9rem;">결제 내역이 없습니다.</p>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-5 text-center text-muted small border-top">
        <p class="fw-medium text-dark mb-1">SEOYEON TOUR</p>
        <p>대표자: 원서연, 정유진</p>
        <p>Tel: 010-2987-7368 · Email: angelo2001@naver.com</p>
        <p class="mt-3">© 2025 Seoyeon Tour. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
